#: ../../source/reference/tensor/generated/maxframe.tensor.special.rgamma.rst:2
msgid "maxframe.tensor.special.rgamma"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.special.gamma_funcs.rgamma:1 of
msgid "Reciprocal of the gamma function."
msgstr "伽马函数的倒数。"

#: maxframe.tensor.special.gamma_funcs.rgamma:3 of
msgid ""
"Defined as :math:`1 / \\Gamma(z)`, where :math:`\\Gamma` is the gamma "
"function. For more on the gamma function see `gamma`."
msgstr ""
"定义为 :math:`1 / \\Gamma(z)`，其中 :math:`\\Gamma` 是伽马函数。有关伽马"
"函数的更多信息，请参见 `gamma`。"

#: ../../source/reference/tensor/generated/maxframe.tensor.special.rgamma.rst
msgid "参数"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.special.gamma_funcs.rgamma:6 of
msgid "Real or complex valued input"
msgstr "实数或复数输入"

#: maxframe.tensor.special.gamma_funcs.rgamma:8 of
msgid "Optional output array for the function results"
msgstr "可选的函数结果输出数组"

#: ../../source/reference/tensor/generated/maxframe.tensor.special.rgamma.rst
msgid "返回"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.special.gamma_funcs.rgamma:11 of
msgid "Function results"
msgstr "函数结果"

#: ../../source/reference/tensor/generated/maxframe.tensor.special.rgamma.rst
msgid "返回类型"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.special.gamma_funcs.rgamma:14 of
msgid ":py:obj:`gamma`, :py:obj:`gammaln`, :py:obj:`loggamma`"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.special.gamma_funcs.rgamma:17 of
msgid "备注"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.special.gamma_funcs.rgamma:18 of
msgid ""
"The gamma function has no zeros and has simple poles at nonpositive "
"integers, so `rgamma` is an entire function with zeros at the nonpositive"
" integers. See the discussion in [dlmf]_ for more details."
msgstr ""
"伽马函数没有零点，在非正整数处有简单极点，因此 `rgamma` 是一个在非正整数"
"处为零的整函数。详见 [dlmf]_ 中的讨论。"

#: maxframe.tensor.special.gamma_funcs.rgamma:24 of
msgid "引用"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.special.gamma_funcs.rgamma:25 of
msgid ""
"Nist, Digital Library of Mathematical functions, "
"https://dlmf.nist.gov/5.2#i"
msgstr "Nist, 数学函数数字图书馆, https://dlmf.nist.gov/5.2#i"

